            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um programa como esse usa o operador <code>==</code> para verificar se a <code>answer</code> de um participante em um quiz de perguntas e respostas está correta.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer == \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;\\(answer) is correct!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"35\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Picasso is correct!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>==</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Wrong answers",
            "id": 126742,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>E se a resposta do quiz de curiosidades não estiver correta? Podemos usar <code>!=</code> para verificar se <code>answer</code> não é igual a <code>\"Picasso\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Matisse&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer != \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(answer + \" /><text value=\"&quot; is wrong!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"answer == &quot;Picasso&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Matisse is wrong!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>answer != \"Picasso\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Different comparisons",
            "id": 126743,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  As declarações <code>if</code> funcionam com todos os operadores de comparação que exploramos até agora. Como verificar se <code>age</code> é maior ou igual a <code>55</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age = \" /><text value=\"75\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"55\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Discount applied&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Discount applied\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>age</code> seguido de <code>&gt;=</code> e finalmente <code>55</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Condition",
            "id": 126744,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  As instruções <code>if</code> não precisam usar um operador especial para comparar variáveis como <code>isDay</code> a valores booleanos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Lights off!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"==\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Lights off!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>isDay</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variables",
            "id": 126745,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para usar o resultado de uma comparação várias vezes, podemos armazená-lo em uma variável como <code>pass</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" score = \" /><text value=\"51\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" pass = score &gt; \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" pass {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(pass)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"44\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>pass</code>.</p></body></html>"
