          {
            "title": "Example: Correct answers",
            "id": 126753,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifique uma condição para sugerir um restaurante se a <code>diet</code> do usuário for igual a <code>vegetarian</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet = \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" veggieRestaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Root&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;DelPosto&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet == \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Try out: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + veggieRestaurant)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"89\" /><option startIndex=\"90\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"!==\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Try out: Root\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>diet</code> seguido de <code>==</code>.</p></body></html>"
